profile.name: Manish Goregaokar
profile.headline: Senior Software Engineer | @google
profile.summary: Highly motivated and experienced software engineer with a strong passion for systems programming. Proven track record of contributing to open-source projects, including ICU4X and Temporal APIs.

experience.title: Senior Software Engineer
description: Designed and implemented multiple features for ICU4X and Temporal APIs using Rust.
Collaborated with cross-functional teams to integrate ICU4X and Temporal APIs into Google's products.

experience.title: Freelance Developer
description: Contributed to open-source projects such as diplomat, rust-url, and triomphe.
Developed and maintained multiple Rust libraries for various clients.

experience.title: Open Source Maintainer
description: Maintained and updated multiple open-source projects, including ICU4X and Temporal APIs.
Collaborated with other maintainers to resolve issues and improve the overall quality of the projects.
